trans-unit.source: Implement and attach to a <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter"></xref> object to control how the importer maps Web Services Description Language (WSDL) parts to those of a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Implementera och ansluta till en <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter"> </xref> objekt att kontrollera hur Importverktyget mappar Web Services WSDL (Description Language) delar med en <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IWsdlImportExtension interface to control the mapping between WSDL and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> objects, especially when reading custom WSDL extensions to modify your contract or endpoint information.
trans-unit.target: Implementera gränssnittet IEsdlImportExtension för att styra mappningen mellan WSDL och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>objekt, särskilt när du läser anpassade WSDL-tillägg till ändrar informationen om kontrakt eller slutpunkt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>

trans-unit.source: Then attach your custom IWsdlImportExtension object to a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter> either programmatically or by using an application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Koppla dina anpassade IEsdlImportExtension objekt till en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>genom programmering eller via en programkonfigurationsfil.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>

trans-unit.source: You can also attach your custom IWsdlImportExtension object to the internal <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter> used by the [ServiceModel Metadata Utility Tool (Svcutil.exe)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) using an application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Du kan även bifoga din anpassade IEsdlImportExtension-objekt till det interna <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>används av den [ServiceModel Metadata för verktyget (Svcutil.exe)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) med hjälp av en programkonfigurationsfil.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> method is called to import a contract.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A>metoden anropas för att importera ett kontrakt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.BeforeImport%2A> method to modify the metadata that is then imported into <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: Använd den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.BeforeImport%2A>metod för att ändra de metadata som sedan importeras till <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>objekt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.BeforeImport%2A>

trans-unit.source: Called prior to importing metadata documents.
trans-unit.target: Anropas innan Importera metadata dokument.

trans-unit.source: The BeforeImport methods of all registered <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension> objects is called before anything is imported from the supplied metadata.
trans-unit.target: BeforeImport-metoder för alla registrerade <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension>objekt anropas innan något har importerats från angivna metadata.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension>
